com.agorapulse.micronaut.amazon.awssdk.dynamodb.annotation

Annotation Type Ignore


  • @Inherited
 @Documented
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value={ANNOTATION_TYPE,FIELD,METHOD})
public @interface Ignore
    Specifies that the attribute should be ignored. This annotation can be used a replacement of DynamoDbIgnore on fields.
